Articles.Content:
Hello Everyone!

This thread is for basically everyone to post their spaceship creations! I will start with mine!

This is a F 15 Eagle I made using stock parts.

https://www.dropbox.com/s/r5nrjsqziked037/Screen%20Shot%202013-06-07%20at%2010.43.46%20PM.png

https://www.dropbox.com/s/i5cdc5q4unmuxap/Screen%20Shot%202013-06-07%20at%2010.44.24%20PM.png

So Here it is if you want to download it!

Link: https://www.dropbox.com/s/cdx7ciyndw1sm9p/F%2015%20Eagle.craft

Note: The F15 needs to go straight off the runway and continue its run onto the beach. Press s the whole takeoff process.

Edited June 8, 2013 by RoyceMingYu
OMG I just realized how similar the shadow was to the real F 15
